  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational study on the efficacy of the secondary placement of the A.M.I Soft
      Gastric Band in weight regain or weight loss failure after lap. gastric bypass.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Unknown status</overall_status>
